    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In stone masonry, courses set at the level of a lintel, commonly differentiated from the wall by their greater projection, finish, or thickness which often match that of the lintel.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
